         As a ZipNews User You're Welcome to Join Us

As the number of users world-wide of ZipNews has grown, the need for an
Internet style mailing list has become apparent.  We have formed one and
you are more than welcome to join it and share ZipNews usage tips, early
information re: coming enhancements, discovery of bugs and workarounds,
etc.

To join the ZipNews Mailing List, send e-mail to:  list-server@nlbbs.com
and include in the message text:

subscribe zipnews-users

You will receive an automated welcoming message with some additional
information about communicating with the group and our list-server.

   - Jack Kilday
     December 5, 1993
